That's not how I wanted you
to meet my mother.

12:37.177 --> 12:38.677
You were thinking
over high tea?

12:38.678 --> 12:40.215
I don't even know what that is.

12:40.216 --> 12:42.649
But don't mix "high"
and anything with my mother.

12:42.650 --> 12:44.517
What did she say to you?
Nothing.

12:44.518 --> 12:46.650
Nothing? You're almost
an hour late for school.

12:46.651 --> 12:49.955
Yeah, but I'm here now. Did you
hear anything from the clinic?

12:49.990 --> 12:51.956
No, I didn't hear anything yet.

12:51.459 --> 12:53.959
And I didn't need you
to add any stress to my day,

12:53.394 --> 12:55.694
while I'm waiting,
by talking to my mother.

12:55.797 --> 12:58.664
I'm sorry. I thought it was
a good thing I got to meet her.

12:59.331 --> 13:00.631
Well, it's not.

