41:48.452 --> 41:51.691
and I wanna be married to the baby's
mother before the baby gets here.

41:52.757 --> 41:53.457
Okay. How about this?

41:53.227 --> 41:55.727
How about if you wait
until the baby's a year old?

41:55.728 --> 41:59.162
If the baby's a year old and you
still wanna do this, then do it.

41:59.163 --> 42:01.430
Just don't do it now.
It's too soon.

42:02.867 --> 42:03.101
A year?

42:03.102 --> 42:05.237
My daughter is supposed
to walk around a year

42:04.571 --> 42:07.205
without knowing her mother
and father are married?

42:07.741 --> 42:09.641
They don't walk the first year.

42:10.178 --> 42:12.277
And she won't know
for a few years.

42:12.278 --> 42:15.178
You have a few years to decide,
if that's your concern.

42:16.180 --> 42:17.180
A few years?

42:17.249 --> 42:19.815
We started at one year,
and now we're at a few years.

42:19.985 --> 42:22.018
Dad, we're moving
in the wrong direction.

42:22.019 --> 42:24.150
All right. A year.
A year after the baby's born.

42:25.058 --> 42:26.458
No. Now.
I wanna get married now.

42:25.958 --> 42:28.058
Does Adrian wanna
get married now?

42:29.062 --> 42:29.662
I'm sure she does.

42:29.797 --> 42:31.997
Have you asked her?
No. I'm asking you first.

42:32.033 --> 42:34.798
You know, if you have to ask
your dad's permission first,

42:34.799 --> 42:36.934
maybe you're just
a little too young.

42:36.935 --> 42:39.168
The groom usually
just asks the bride's father.

42:39.472 --> 42:41.539
I'll get to that.
And, you know, next year,

42:41.540 --> 42:43.673
I'm 18, and I won't need
your permission.

42:43.942 --> 42:45.976
No, you won't.
So wait till next year.

42:46.477 --> 42:48.444
No, I'm not waiting
until next year.

42:49.612 --> 42:51.079
Dad, please.
Please, Dad.

42:51.581 --> 42:53.082
This is my life.
It's my life.

42:53.083 --> 42:55.150
I wanna share it
with Adrian and our daughter.

42:56.489 --> 42:58.255
You know it's
the right thing to do.

42:58.061 --> 43:00.361
Her father knows it's
the right thing to do.

42:59.929 --> 43:03.796
I know it's the right thing
to do. Just let me get married.

